EN: So this is the last outfit from my Gossengold Theme Week.
I hope you enjoyed it and I really liked this idea. Would you want me to continue such a Theme Week, but with other labels like 5Preview or Blackmilk?
Just tell me what you think about that :)
btw this is my last outfit video with this kind of structure so stay tuned what comes next :)
